---
import Section from '../shared/Section.astro';
import SectionTitle from '../shared/SectionTitle.astro';
import Card from '../shared/Card.astro';
---

<Section bg="secondary">
  <SectionTitle label="The problem">
    Why most cloud-native journeys fail
  </SectionTitle>

  <div class="reveal-children grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
    <Card>
      <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 text-red-400">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M10 4v6m0 4h.01M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Analysis paralysis</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        1,000+ CNCF projects. Every vendor claims to be the answer. Internal teams lack the experience to evaluate, select, and architect a coherent platform.
      </p>
    </Card>

    <Card>
      <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-400">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M13 7l-3 3m0 0l-3-3m3 3V3m7 7a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Integration hell</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        Even organizations that pick the right technologies fail at making them work together. Security gaps. No tested DR. Upgrades that break integrations. Alert storms nobody understands.
      </p>
    </Card>

    <Card>
      <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-yellow-500/10 text-yellow-400">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M8 8v4m0 4h.01M4 4h12a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Manual operations at scale</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        Dozens of components means hundreds of CRDs, thousands of metrics, and endless upgrade coordination. Manual runbooks cannot keep pace. You need infrastructure that is designed to be operated by AI.
      </p>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-border-primary bg-bg-primary p-6 text-center reveal">
    <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
      <span class="text-accent font-medium">Dozens of components working in harmony</span>, operated with
      <span class="text-accent font-medium">AI precision</span>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>
